{"tid":1183214,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人龍舟P, 窮拎勿入。","createTime":"2019-06-02T18:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T05:00:24.000Z","uid":5190,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"95d6b20aaa69c8492ed1fd5087892a6fd3a737e3","tid":1183214,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:09:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。夜晚出海。 <br />\n我地book 了3 隻龍舟。第一隻 神龍出航 , 租的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/88/59264cff6357c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F88%2F59264cff6357c.jpg&h=7e637e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐23人的，長50幾呎。<br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的 龍的傳人 坐10人 日式龍舟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/05/04/realtime/6258457.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F05%2F04%2Frealtime%2F6258457.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=30942041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2367337_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2367337_2.jpg&h=71ef9168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-03-25/656/20180325002789.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-03-25%2F656%2F20180325002789.jpg&h=be347850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。<br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。 <br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多傻。 <br />\n<br />\n星期五 , 7點尖沙咀碼頭集合 <br />\n<br />\n男仔：$1000 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1000去龍舟河的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d龍舟河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"08ea6ae490fdc8369047c4fe09c7968a923eaaa6","tid":1183214,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:10:04.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"77a36de281f735687330020cb377ede42c467cad","tid":1183214,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:11:29.000Z","msg":"留低聯絡方式 謝謝"},{"pid":"21df61a23c77eb4383bbb8ca3e96d9f3bd5ab448","tid":1183214,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a36de281f735687330020cb377ede42c467cad","tid":1183214,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:11:29.000Z","msg":"留低聯絡方式 謝謝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:12:02.000Z","msg":"有意去 請留下tg"},{"pid":"acde2b58a8b4953c62bbb7db7c73065f4d314901","tid":1183214,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"買我"},{"pid":"d5171a7b25c8f4d382af4126f3656adb89644fd5","tid":1183214,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21df61a23c77eb4383bbb8ca3e96d9f3bd5ab448","tid":1183214,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a36de281f735687330020cb377ede42c467cad","tid":1183214,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:11:29.000Z","msg":"留低聯絡方式 謝謝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:12:02.000Z","msg":"有意去 請留下tg"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"沒有tg"},{"pid":"a50dbe95a308ede57fd150beb639e1d087b71834","tid":1183214,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5171a7b25c8f4d382af4126f3656adb89644fd5","tid":1183214,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21df61a23c77eb4383bbb8ca3e96d9f3bd5ab448","tid":1183214,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a36de281f735687330020cb377ede42c467cad","tid":1183214,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":